                    </div>
                    <div class="content__right">
                      <div class="content__main">
                        <p>“For me, Peru is the molten core of South America, a distillation of the oldest traditions and the
                          finest building, weaving and art made by the most sophisticated cultures on the continent. In Peru the
                          wildest landscapes – from frozen Andean peaks to the deep Amazon – help us re-forge our connection to
                          the natural world. It is also a cultural stew, where diverse peoples live side by side, negotiating
                          modern life with humor and aplomb. Beyond that, the cuisine alone makes it worth the trip. Every return
                          is rich and surprising.”</p>
                        <p>– Carolyn McCarthy</p>
                      </div>
